{"word":"H3467 - יָשַׁע - yâshaʻ - yaw-shah' - [idiom] at all","slug":"H3467","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָשַׁע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâshaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-shah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] at all"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E2; - ya&#x0302;sha&#x201B;</b> - <i>yaw-shah'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>be open</i>, <i>wide</i> or <i>free</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>be safe</i>; causatively to <i>free</i> or <i>succor: - </i> X at all, avenging, defend, deliver (-er), help, preserve, rescue, be safe, bring (having) salvation, save (-iour), get victory."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1954\">H1954</a>, <a href=\"#/H1955\">H1955</a>, <a href=\"#/H3444\">H3444</a>, <a href=\"#/H3468\">H3468</a>, <a href=\"#/H3469\">H3469</a>, <a href=\"#/H3470\">H3470</a>, <a href=\"#/H3471\">H3471</a>, <a href=\"#/H4190\">H4190</a>, <a href=\"#/H4337\">H4337</a>, <a href=\"#/H4338\">H4338</a>, <a href=\"#/H7769\">H7769</a>, <a href=\"#/H7770\">H7770</a>, <a href=\"#/H7771\">H7771</a>, <a href=\"#/H7774\">H7774</a>, <a href=\"#/H8668\">H8668</a>"}]}